	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have achieved a position of considerable esteem in the ranks of your deity’s faithful, and your power only grows. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Intelligence or Wisdom score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die in the Religion skill or your existing expertise die increases by 1 step. Your maximum expertise die size for Religion is a d10.</p></li><li><p>Choose a cleric spell of up to 4th-level with at least one rare variant. You learn a rare variant of the selected spell for free. You only need to prepare the base version of the selected spell and can choose to cast either the rare or base variant when casting it. </p></li></ul>",
